f. Licensed Rights means the rights granted to You subject to the terms and conditions of this Public License, which are limited to all Copyright and Similar Rights that apply to Your use of the Licensed Material and are not limited by Exceptions and Limitations.
g. Licensor means the individual(s) or entity(ies) granting rights under this Public License.
